      • isOwnedBy

        public boolean isOwnedBy(java.lang.Thread t)
        Description copied from interface: OwnableModule
        This method determines whether this is currently owned by Thread t. Should return true if t == null and this is not owned. If the owner of this died, it is not owned.
        Specified by:
        isOwnedBy in interface OwnableModule
        Parameters:
        t - The Thread to check ownership for.
        Returns:
        true if t == the Thread that owns this (or t == null and this is not owned), false otherwise.

        Acquires ownership of this for t if: (no Thread currently owns this, or force == true), and t doesn't already own this. Returns the results of this.isOwnedBy(t). Note: t can be null if you are attempting to force ownership relinquishing.
        Specified by:
        acquireOwnershipFor in interface OwnableModule
        Parameters:
